flowchart TD
    A[Employee Question] --> B[Retrieve Top Chunks]
    B --> C[Trusted Context: policy excerpts]
    C --> D[Grounded Prompt: rules + context]
    D --> E[Generated Answer: cites sources]
    E --> F[Evaluation: Recall@K + MRR]

    G[(Policy Corpus)] --> H[Chunking]
    H --> I[Embeddings]
    I --> J[(ChromaDB Vector Store)]
    J --> B

    B -. failure point .-> K[Wrong source retrieved]
    D -. failure point .-> L[Weak grounding instruction]
    E -. failure point .-> M[Unsupported answer]

